      <p style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #444444; margin: 0 0 28px 0;">Cheshire house prices vary from £103,000 for a Halton flat to £1,163,360 for an Alderley Edge detached home (ONS Dec 2025, Rightmove Feb 2026). Six questions cover the most common comparisons, budgets, and affordability areas.</p>
